EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO DELINQUENT AND DEPENDENT CHILDREN -- PROCEEDINGS IN
FAMILY COURT
***
1 This act would establish concurrent jurisdiction between the Rhode Island Family Court
2 and the Federal Government for the purposes of adjudicating minors who have allegedly committed
3 a crime on a military installation located in the State of Rhode Island.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
